I would consider my self to be quite decent at pvp but sadly over half of my deaths are from either team spleef or my computer crashing.  If you want to keep up to date with what i'm up to make sure to subscribe to me on YouTube and follow me on twitter and If your ever bored and just want to hang out, add me on skype but make sure to put your IGN and say that your from Nebula in the contact request.  Well thats it about me, I'll see  you around!
